texts.desc:
①：Activate 1 of these effects (but you can only use each of these effects of this card's name once per turn);
● Add 1 card that mentions "Dark Time Wizard" from your Deck to your hand, except "Dark Time Wizard", also add 1 "Dark Time Wizard" from your GY to your hand during the End Phase of this turn.
● Toss a coin and call it. If you call it right, destroy as many monsters your opponent controls as possible, and if you do, inflict damage to them equal to half those monsters' total original ATK. If you call it wrong, destroy all monsters you control.
